'''''N''-2-吡啶基-2-吡啶硫代甲酰胺'''是一种有机化合物，化学式为C<sub>11</sub>H<sub>9</sub>N<sub>3</sub>S，它可由[[2-氨基吡啶|2-氨基吡啶]]、[[2-甲基吡啶|2-甲基吡啶]]和[[硫|硫]]在160 °C反应得到。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Autophagy|volume=15|issue=2|language=en|issn=1554-8627|date=2019-02-01|pages=295–311|doi=10.1080/15548627.2018.1517073|url=https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/full/10.1080/15548627.2018.1517073|title=Discovery of a small molecule targeting autophagy via ATG4B inhibition and cell death of colorectal cancer cells in vitro and in vivo|accessdate=2020-11-25|author=Yuanyuan Fu, Liang Hong, Jiecheng Xu, Guoping Zhong, Qiong Gu, Qianqian Gu, Yanping Guan, Xueping Zheng, Qi Dai, Xia Luo, Cui Liu, Zhiying Huang, Xiao-Ming Yin, Peiqing Liu, Min Li|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114195308/https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/full/10.1080/15548627.2018.1517073|dead-url=no}}</ref>它可以和[[氯金酸|氯金酸]]反应，生成2-(2-吡啶基)[1,2,4]噻二唑并[2,3-''a'']吡啶-4-鎓四氯金酸盐。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Inorganica Chimica Acta|volume=363|issue=1|language=en|date=2010-01|pages=41–48|doi=10.1016/j.ica.2009.10.003|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S002016930900591X|title=The cycloauration of pyridine-2-thiocarboxamide ligands|accessdate=2020-11-25|author=Kelly J. Kilpin, William Henderson, Brian K. Nicholson|archive-date=2020-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200209063719/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S002016930900591X|dead-url=no}}</ref>

